SILVA release 123 is available under

http://www.arb-silva.de/no_cache/download/archive/release_123/

There are two options:

1) Download ARB database file

   http://www.arb-silva.de/fileadmin/silva_databases/release_123/ARB_files/SSURef_NR99_123_SILVA_12_07_15_opt.arb.tgz

   and then use ARB export feature or ARB-SATIVA to obtain the alignment (the way I used)

OR

2) Download FASTA file 

http://www.arb-silva.de/fileadmin/silva_databases/release_123/Exports/SILVA_123_SSURef_Nr99_tax_silva_full_align_trunc.fasta.gz


